Automatic lighting control using PIR & IR sensors

Automatic fan speed control using LM35/thermistor

Power-saving of up to 86% per tube light

Delay-based light OFF mechanism

Suitable for classrooms, labs, corridors, offices

No manual switch required

Highly reliable system with relay safety features

** Customization **

You can customize:

Time delay before switching OFF lights

Temperature threshold for fan activation

Number of sensors based on room size

Fan speed levels instead of simple ON/OFF

Dual sensor entry-exit counting

** Further Customization **

Advanced additions:

IoT integration (mobile control & monitoring)

Smart energy logging with cloud dashboards

Automatic day/night detection using LDR

Classroom occupancy counter (accurate human count)

Voice control system using Google Assistant/Alexa

Replace relay with TRIAC for smooth fan speed control
